549
00:26:07,900 --> 00:26:11,236
- Fluffy times fluffy.
- For sure.

550
00:26:13,605 --> 00:26:18,410
And our cute and fluffy Shoppi
is going to eat it.

551
00:26:18,477 --> 00:26:20,045
- Wild, huh?
