576
00:27:22,841 --> 00:27:24,309
I see.

577
00:27:30,048 --> 00:27:31,216
This is good!

578
00:27:31,850 --> 00:27:33,118
I'm glad.

579
00:27:33,185 --> 00:27:35,554
- You do like sweets.
- I like sweets.

580
00:27:36,622 --> 00:27:38,624
Try the middle here, Shoppi.

581
00:27:38,690 --> 00:27:40,626
- Dig in like a cave.
